        google: { rating: 4.8, review_count: 1805, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=16301358963119768773&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'TorPez', rating: 5, text: 'Chris provided me with the most outstanding customer service I have ever received. He was above and beyond in every expectation. I never left a shop in such a good mood. He knows how to treat his customers correct. Shout out to you Chris!! A real one', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Heidi Graham', rating: 5, text: 'You park. There\'s accessible parking spots. You walk in and two people are able to get your license checked. There\'s a bathroom and water fountain on your right. Walking in, I swear we must have been there on the first day, it was so packed in there. But so many people were able to help my partner. I sat in a wide butt chair that they had available, which I really appreciated! They have this autom', time: '6 months ago'}, {author: 'Dana Platt-Nelson', rating: 5, text: 'What a great experience! From the moment I walked in, the front desk gentleman was so polite and made me feel welcome right away. He also made sure to ask if it was my first time in, which it was. Then their kiosks to place your order are super user friendly. Very clean in there too.  Next I got in the checkout line and Matt helped me right away. What a guy! Super upbeat and just one of those guys', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Samantha Vermeire', rating: 5, text: 'I love this location everyone is always so helpful and extremely kind. Marcie was so nice and helpful making sure I had all my questions answered and always having a smile on her face! Highly recommend RISE to anyone!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Extacy Figueroa', rating: 5, text: 'As a med patient this location tends to be the fastest and most efficient with orders. I’ve gone to almost every other location rose has in Minnesota and this is the best. Usually have amazing deals for med patients also. Chris was absolutely amazing today got me in and out so fast so was the front end workers.', time: '3 months ago'}] }
