        google: { rating: 4.2, review_count: 33, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=6440815746135753304&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Brandanna J S Anderson', rating: 5, text: 'I snuck around and found out. They grow dank and have super good equipment for testing and extracting. It\'s really not that expensive, no FedTax. Honestly the flowers are pretty fire. Carts are slammin\' If you\'re at the casino you might as well stop by. Everyone who works there is rad. See for yourself...', time: '4 months ago'}, {author: 'Tyler Quam', rating: 3, text: 'Yes price is high, but it’s legal pot with state tax. What do you expect? Not a lot of options to choose from. I’ve smoked a bowl and it got me what I would expect from any other bud. Not a bad experience. Was it worth the price? No. But quick and easy shopping. Overall it wasn’t a bad experience.', time: '8 months ago'}, {author: 'Kelvin Higgins', rating: 5, text: 'I\'d have go argue that they sell some of the best weed in the state if you get there higher thc buds they will give the rise medical dispensary a run for there money and there bud is very comparable to the rhythm brand that rise sells the other tribal dispensarys sell some ditch weed not these guys they try to put there name behind a good product', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'Justin B.', rating: 5, text: 'You guys rock! The flower you sell is by far the best. Highly recommend!! Got tired of spending money on flower that is dried out at the brainerd dispensary.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'kevin', rating: 4, text: 'Great pre-rolls honestly my favorite style, nice round joint style not cones and good tasty bud. Very nice pre-rolls compared to the other shops around town these ones burn nice. Would have given you five stars but your prices are outrageous.', time: '7 months ago'}] }
