        google: { rating: 4.8, review_count: 46, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=497623207070150284&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Ali Albattat', rating: 5, text: 'Easily one of the coolest dispensaries I’ve been to. The shop is awesome, the products are top-tier, and you can tell they’re only going to keep getting better. Grabbed some great glass and gummies — highly recommend stopping by.', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'Natalie Campion', rating: 5, text: 'I’ve visited Frostbite three times and I can confirm it’s the best dispensary experience I’ve had in Minnesota. They have a warm and inviting waiting area with a seamless check in. The dispensary itself is designed beautifully with digital menus the scroll through their product selection and windows that let the sunshine in. The staff is knowledgeable and made great recommendations about products ', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Aubrey Lee', rating: 5, text: 'I’ve been checking out different dispensaries lately, and I had a great experience at this little spot! I was met with friendly & knowledgeable staff & loved looking at some really cool pieces that looked like they were flipped from old vases & things of the sort. I’ll definitely be stopping in again soon. :)', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Anna Morales Koehler', rating: 5, text: 'So excited to have this place nearby!   MUCH more convenient (ie location, shopping experience) than others I’ve been to in the cities.  Everyone was so friendly and helpful with all of my questions, and I didn’t feel rushed at all.  I’m new to vape products, and they walked me through everything.  Can’t wait to go back for some flower!', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'Mark Ehoff', rating: 5, text: 'I have been waiting for a dispensary to open in my area and Frostbite has answered the call! Everyone I spoke with was very helpful and friendly with all the questions I had. The product selection and pricing was good. I picked up a vape, edibles, and some merchandise. Overall it was a great experience.', time: '2 months ago'}] }
