        initial: 'AC',
        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/404/749/avatar/1770330973-acc-round-logo.jpg",
        google: { rating: 3.4, review_count: 45, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=12807132684912385809&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Bill Shore', rating: 5, text: 'The people here are amazing. They are super friendly, all seem to enjoy being there, and were very helpful with any questions I had.  On top of that I went in one day while their systems were down and they immediately gave me a 20% off coupon just because they felt bad. I then lost that coupon, and they still honored it.  Yes it’s 60 bucks an eighth. But it’s including tax. Every other review sayi', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Mikey Nitro', rating: 5, text: 'Much better selection and price than other local chain shops. Friendly staff that are very knowledgeable and happy to talk bud with ya. I recommend Anoka C.C. to anyone that currently uses other facilities.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'PT', rating: 4, text: 'The store looked great and felt more welcoming than other places I’ve visited around the cities. I picked up some gummies and a preroll on my first visit. So far, so good. Vape cartridge prices are pretty high right now so maybe wait on that until it comes down. Overall, a good experience.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Robot_Squirrel', rating: 3, text: 'Be prepared to spend 45 minutes before you even get to look at the products  The prices are high compared to any other dispensary I\'ve been to.  I thought the selection was quite good.  A lot of variety of flower.  My biggest problem is that the building seems like it was designed by someone who has no working knowledge of a dispensary.  The id scan barely works, the lobby can only fit 8 people co', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Aidan Dailey', rating: 5, text: 'People you gotta check this joint out, really friendly staff. good environment and products if you live close to Anoka or in Anoka county give these guys a try don\'t listen to the bad reviews the shop is brand new and others think its going to be a 5 star shop in just a week or two. it takes time and for new products to arrive. Thank you Anoka cannabis I will be visiting again soon.', time: 'a month ago'}] }
