        initial: 'LC',
        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/396/232/avatar/1775599694-duluth-logo-weedmaps.png",
        google: { rating: 4.1, review_count: 131, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=6765514405281286692&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Tina Marie', rating: 3, text: 'This place was nice, awesome wall murals, very friendly staff at the counter. My only issues was at the door it states the different type of IDs needed to get past and Tribal ID was at the top of that list. I handed the young man working my Tribal ID, he looked at it and said this do you have something else? I told him this is a Federal Accepted ID but he continued to tell me it would take to long', time: '6 months ago'}, {author: 'Dylan Ray', rating: 1, text: 'Okay, where to start... Prices? ABSURD. Service? Non-existent. Knowledge? Oh please. They put directly on their menu "taxes need to be lowered", yet they\'re charging $70 for a one gram vape cart. 6 dispensaries in Michigan (2 hours east) run vape carts for at most $40, but that\'s live resin and top grade. But at most of them, Regular carts are $40 for SIX OF THEM. Then the cashier has the audacity', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Tracy Ashley', rating: 5, text: '⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Outstanding Experience!  We stopped in yesterday to Legacy Cannabis in Duluth and were blown away by the customer service. The store has such a cool vibe...great music, awesome mural, and an overall welcoming atmosphere. Lacey and Corey were incredible! Both were extremely knowledgeable, friendly, and patient. They took the time to explain products, answer questions, and make sure we le', time: '4 months ago'}, {author: 'Amanda Johnson', rating: 5, text: 'Took a trip up North to ride out at Spirt Mtn (rad spot) and had to stop at Legacy up here (love there Woodbury dispensary). Blown away again by this location - amazing budtenders who actually know about cannabis (rare in my experiences across the country). We talked terps, strains, grow tecnhinques! They just got in some live resin carts which were DELICIOUS and so glad they have options that are', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Eric Sharp', rating: 5, text: 'What a great place the service is great and very knowledgeable. I will be returning for more visits.', time: '2 months ago'}] }
