        google: { rating: 4.2, review_count: 50, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=11331542417030810410&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Kevin Defoe', rating: 5, text: 'Great staff and very knowledgeable on their really good products. Selection has improved. Order online early in the day to make sure you get what you want, seems to sell fast. 1/8THS ARE 4GS HERE (not 3.5g like at other dispos).', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Adam', rating: 4, text: 'Nice little dispensary located in the Hinckley Grand Casino parking lot. Everyone is super nice! Selection is limited. No concentrates available yet. The carts are distillate only and super expensive. No live rosin carts. The flower and pre-rolls are good, but prices are a bit high. I\'m sure as more dispensaries come online, prices will self regulate. All in all it\'s a nice dispensary if you\'re in', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'Anthony McGannon (Elune)', rating: 3, text: 'The service was good, but they sold me a broken bowl with my pipe. It was clearly inspected by the cashier and I was in a hurry so I did not doubt them, I got home excited to try it out, only to realize the bowl was broken. I live an hour away so I cannot get it replaced, I\'m quite a bit disappointed.', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Forrest St John', rating: 5, text: 'Came in around thanksgiving. Nice little dispensary. Very beautiful & very knowledgeable young lady behind tha glass helping. Fast service. Nothing to complain about!', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Bomaye Productions', rating: 1, text: 'ABSOLUTELY RIDICULOUS . they’re hours on google need to be changed. i drove an hour here in a storm just for them to be closed at 6pm. on top of that they only accept cash , so they make you take money from an atm ( that charges you $5 ) their weed is decent but 100% not worth the price, hassle, and inconsistency of them being open.  do better.', time: '4 months ago'}] }
