        google: { rating: 3.9, review_count: 139, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=14914660037054939539&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Sabrina Hollis', rating: 5, text: 'My husband and I have gone into this dispensary several times and love the prices, deals offered and great product. Yesterday we went to their event “Vape and Bingo” and it was a BLAST! The ladies working kept it fun, the bingo was so exciting, there was drawings and the prizes were crazy good! 10/10 recommend going, We will definitely be going again their next event .', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Alicia Rux', rating: 5, text: 'Thief River Falls dispensary is what a dispensary SHOULD be. They got a cool, chill vibe, music, TV screens going, and super friendly, helpful employees who are clearly genuinely having a good time.  I don\'t even want to post about their deals because... well... you can just find that out for yourself. 😬  Oh, and it smells really good. Thanks guys!!!👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Justin Gunn', rating: 5, text: 'Very courteous staff, Ian was the best, even helped me select replacements. Place your order, pay, and check out the merchandise while you wait. Flower looked amazing. Stop in and get yours today! Quality of product is verified. Enjoy.', time: '2 years ago'}, {author: 'Robert Selbitschka', rating: 5, text: 'What a wonderful experience I had at Nativecare! There was a long line and i expected that, we arrived at 2:20pm and got in line. We were told we could be turned away as they were closing at 6pm however, the staff were super generous and didn\'t take breaks and served not only us 20 minutes after close but a huge line that formed behind us. Fed us hotdogs and cookies while waiting, water was also a', time: '2 years ago'}, {author: 'Paul', rating: 1, text: 'The couple of types of bud I have bought from here have been moldy smelly and tasting. They are quite damp and have not been properly cured. It is quite disgusting that they would even try to pass these off to customers. The prices are also insane. Just take a short drive up to Michigan and get some quality stuff for a tenth of the price.', time: '4 months ago'}] }
