        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/378/782/avatar/1742226416-waabigwan-logos-moorhead.png",
        google: { rating: 4.5, review_count: 617, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=3547184175043338492&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Nevaeh Hiner', rating: 4, text: 'The most similar to dispensary\'s in New Jersey or Michigan that ive seen in Missouri so far. The shop is so cute and everyone is very helpful! If you like getting in and out fast or looking around at merch this is a good one :)', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Mar', rating: 4, text: 'Nice clean store, well organized with limited stock in flowers and plenty of accessories to expand your options. Displays are easy to view.  The price is a bit higher than other dispensaries in MN but not by much, and the quality is the same. Everyone is polite and helpful. The glass jars with wood caps are 😎 cool.  Always check the dates of your flowers. Nobody wants to smoke🚫 old buds. See photo', time: '7 months ago'}, {author: 'Roman Carrillo-Olson', rating: 5, text: 'Amazingly friendly staff! Every time I come in they let me know what specials they have on right away before I even order. Anytime I have a question, they answer it very quickly and with rather high accuracy. Prices are a bit high but with Marijuana legalization, that’s something you just have to deal with but the flower makes the price all so worth it!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Loo Lynn', rating: 4, text: 'Great quality flower!! I often get the flower here and it’s fantastic, * NOT COMPLAINING! I LOVE THIS PLACE JUST SOMETHING FOR CONSIDERATION : unfortunately I do not recommend the pre rolls if you’re not too good with your hands. They are packed not consistently, often too tight or packed too small, I’ve noticed the length of the rolls all differ, some are small some are long??. They’re very hard ', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Xyphix', rating: 2, text: 'It’s a great atmosphere in the building, everyone is friendly, but I paid $49 for a .5g cart that wasn’t even full when I opened it. I absolutely got completely ripped off, it wouldn’t be so bad because the cart itself is decent but the fact I paid that much to not even get a full one.', time: 'a month ago'}] }
