        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/044/504/avatar/1712256094-primary-yellow-and-navy-gg-dispensary-logo-stacked-copy_1_.png",
        google: { rating: 4.5, review_count: 537, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=7933414849939715314&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'M T', rating: 1, text: 'I am from Los Angeles and I was under the assumption that all dispensaries are the same.  I found out that is not true! The one thing this place has going for them is the staff. Green Goods has an incredibly kind,  helpful and wonderful staff. They are truly nice to interact with after a long day of work. The facility itself is also really clean.  The prices, the quality and the availability is de', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Raven Turner', rating: 1, text: 'Been here a couple times. I don\'t actually dislike this place that much, but I used to live in WA and it doesn\'t feel very personable in comparison to that. Maybe that\'s also just my personal experience, but between that and the very clearly AI responses to reviews, as sometimes the responses are the exact same and reference "words of encouragement" in positive reviews, for example, even if there ', time: '4 weeks ago'}, {author: 'HeyHo AO', rating: 4, text: 'Clean, courteous, quick, efficient, and a real friendly knowledgeable staff.  Large selection on the Medical side with weekly deals making the pricing  more comparable to a competitive market.  Selection on the recreational adult can be slim and I think just a bit pricey.  I only purchase flower from the medical side.  Selection is solid, and their homegrown product Vireo is sun grown which to me ', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'JayJ', rating: 4, text: 'Staff is awesome. The process is seamless and that\'s such a big value. The vibe is amazing and the place is very clean. The product is always quality. My only thing is recreational seems to be an afterthought. Then online they flash offer you strains and discounts that don\'t apply to you...prices can be high.', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Chloe Billings', rating: 4, text: 'Staff is laid back and knowledgeable. Shopping medical is easy-peasy and usually super quick! Always satisfied with the quality of their products. Not so much with the prices of said products, but I think that’s just how high they have to mark it all because of how our state is. Idk  🤷🏻‍♀️', time: 'a month ago'}] }
