        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/306/254/avatar/1712255555-primary-yellow-and-navy-gg-dispensary-logo-stacked-copy_1_.png",
        google: { rating: 4.4, review_count: 744, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=1526852106365911449&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'harlan prine', rating: 1, text: 'Only game in town so far. Last time I went unknown to me, I had to make 2 separate transactions to get the discounts I shopped for. That created a lot of embarrassment and I felt threatened. The Manager came out and cleared thing up.  She seemed objective and knowledgeable.  And the staff learned.  Why can\'t some have more patience?  They get violent when you ask a question by having a large man h', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Kabrina Alderton', rating: 5, text: 'Been going here for over year for my 5 year old son who is a medical patient & now am a medical patient myself. I love the pharmacists who consult with me to pick the right products for our medical needs and the staff on site is always easy to work with and kind. I never get any of the mild sass that is so common these days at all types of businesses.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Trey Marbury', rating: 5, text: 'They were absolutely amazing they helped us fast and worked well with our needs they were very fast and professional! We love GREEN GOODS!', time: '6 months ago'}, {author: 'Cheryl Hoffman', rating: 5, text: 'I cannot say enough wonderful things about the Blaine Green Goods and its staff. Always pleasant and friendly. Clean inside and out. The vibes are always good at Green Goods. My only wish is to have a dispensary in the Brainerd Lakes area. I drive down 2.5 hours just to get my medicine. That’s how good they are there.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Debra Rodrique', rating: 5, text: 'The staff is very nice and knowledgeable. The process is very easy and if you don\'t know what to do next, the staff will gladly help you on what to do next. I buy medical flower, pre-rolled, and gummies and everything has been excellent. They usually have a wide variety of products to choose from. I would recommend green goods to everyone!!', time: 'a month ago'}] }
