        initial: 'GG',
        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/306/255/avatar/1712255788-primary-yellow-and-navy-gg-dispensary-logo-stacked-copy_1_.png",
        google: { rating: 4.7, review_count: 368, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=18251015212855456438&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Jennifer Herrick', rating: 4, text: 'I really like the staff at my local Green Goods! Overall it\'s a very good experience. However, as someone with MCAS/MCS I wish that they would remove their synthetic scented products such as the Febreeze in the bathroom. :(  I am incredibly sensitive to synthetic fragrances and after using the bathroom yesterday I became ill and could smell it on my jacket for the rest of the day. I had to wash it', time: '3 months ago'}, {author: 'Rogue Obst (RogueRat)', rating: 5, text: 'Top tier product and service, best in hermantown for stock updates on website and services in store, I have never left a store happier. Staff is very friendly and smile at each person creating a relaxing environment,as well as being helpful and kind. Highly suggest for beginners and old-timers alike.', time: '5 months ago'}, {author: 'Casey Mattson.', rating: 5, text: 'Love this place the staff is amazing and they are so knowledgeable. Always quick and easy to get in to and out. The store is so nice and clean', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Jessi Johnson', rating: 5, text: 'Staff is super friendly, checkout was fast and easy. This maybe my favorite location, definitely coming back!!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Dr Doom', rating: 3, text: 'I\'ve made a few purchases here. The store is decent and the staff is friendly. The prices are much too expensive though. The THC in the flower they offer is usually low also. I started driving to Cloquet for purchases, because I get double what my money\'s worth. Bottom line, the product here is way overpriced. I can get an OZ in Cloquet, for the price of a half OZ at this store. It\'s worth the dri', time: 'a month ago'}] }
