        google: { rating: 4.7, review_count: 897, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=17509242439144634722&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Gabriel Watkins', rating: 5, text: 'First time there, and it was a great experience. Had to show my ID way more than I\'m used to at a dispensary, but whatever, just do yourself a favor and keep it out. Once in the door, everyone greeting me was very friendly. I was partnered with a "weed guy" named Josh. He was cool, and it made the shopping go quick and smooth, what I want. Josh was easy to talk to and tell him what I wanted. I wor', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Jennifer Demery', rating: 5, text: 'Staff was amazing, friendly and very knowledgeable about products. Always greeted with kindness and they have a good sense of humor. Have only purchased pre-rolls but will come back for sure', time: '6 months ago'}, {author: 'Dylan Dean', rating: 5, text: 'Joshua was extremely knowledgeable and exceedingly helpful. He was able to explain all of the items we bought and how they functioned along with helping us find the best deal we could get! 10/10 will buy through him every time!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Nina', rating: 5, text: 'A huge Thank You to Budtender; Kelsey!! She is so knowledgeable!! Because of Kelsey I enjoyed my 1st retail shopping experience. She guided me through making choices, as well as she got me a great price by offering what’s on special. I am an absolutely thrilled Customer!', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Maret', rating: 5, text: 'I have always had a very friendly and pleasant experience at the St. Cloud Waabigwan Dispensary! 🌿 The staff is incredibly friendly, welcoming, knowledgeable, and quite helpful in finding exactly what you\'re looking for, whether you\'re a newbie or experienced🌬🍃. I\'m  impressed with all the different product selections available and the fun atmosphere. I have zero complaints; their products are hig', time: 'a month ago'}] }
