        gradient: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #9f1239, #e11d48)',
        initial: 'WM',
        img: "https://images.weedmaps.com/dispensaries/000/378/708/avatar/1742226348-waabigwan-logos-mahnomen.png",
        google: { rating: 4.5, review_count: 339, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=6032278504518993140&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Angel Townsend', rating: 5, text: 'Best dispensary hands down. The staff if very attentive and makes sure you leave with what you want. They don’t force anything on you. I really love going here. #myfavoriteplace', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'drake maye jones', rating: 1, text: 'So I just started going here just to see what’s up since they don’t have vapes it’s the carts only so my first purchase was good but I thought the oil was stuck at the top. But I went to buy another one and this time I waited kept it stand up and unopened did not smoke anything yet. First pic is from your company the second all white vape is from another. I paid 80 dollars for carts with less oil ', time: '5 months ago'}, {author: 'Mitchell Paradise', rating: 2, text: 'I want to love this place. The staff is awesome; good vibes, good service. But I was shorted on my last purchase. So now I can’t go back, ‘cause thems the rules. I used to go in there for the one-gram pre rolls when they sometimes put them on sale for $6 (Which is around $9 after taxes and fees.) I bought fifteen of them and every one of them was light. The fullest one had .72 grams in it, and the', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Justin Smith', rating: 5, text: 'Pretty nice shop. They had product on display. It was nice to be able to see it before I bought it. I\'ll definitely be back.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Ahmad Muhammad', rating: 5, text: 'Love the initial experience. Definitely recommend for anybody who\'s just trying or looking for something different. Great place', time: '2 months ago'}] }
