        google: { rating: 5, review_count: 63, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=4376242277076866997&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Garth Algar', rating: 5, text: 'Love this place and so happy they are in the area, this is my favorite dispensary. The customer service is hands down the best. Staff are friendly and answer questions to make sure you get the right products. Just got the Soap and Lit OG flower, loving both for flavor and effects.', time: '3 weeks ago'}, {author: 'Ryan Sollinger', rating: 5, text: 'Absolutely incredible shop! I\'ll be coming here from now on! Great selection and super friendly staff!', time: '2 months ago'}, {author: 'Sophie Hoiseth', rating: 5, text: 'Britt is super knowledgeable and has a focus on helping people love happier and healthier lives. If you’re new to the benefits of CBD, I’d recommend stopping in and asking questions. Really awesome!', time: '3 years ago'}, {author: 'Matt Wenschlag', rating: 3, text: 'The only reason that this place is getting a low star at least for now is because they have their prices way too damn high who wants to buy a $20 gram of flower or a $20 pre-roll. If the city is screwing you over that much for taxes that you need to price it that much then maybe you should have another meeting with the city Chamber of Commerce', time: '3 weeks ago'}, {author: 'Cameron Montgomery', rating: 5, text: 'I had an awesome experience here. The ladies that helped me were super kind and helped find exactly what I needed. Worked great too. Great products, great prices, super friendly services. Highly recommend checking it out! New favorite store in town:)', time: 'a year ago'}] }
