        google: { rating: 4.7, review_count: 34, maps_url: 'https://maps.google.com/?cid=12357543422035386426&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA', reviews: [{author: 'Trey Keuten', rating: 5, text: 'If you’re looking for a smoke shop that goes above and beyond, look no further than this gem in Two Harbors! I can’t say enough good things about this place. The owners and staff are incredible—they genuinely care about their customers. Every visit is met with a warm smile and a level of kindness that’s rare to find these days.  They’re always willing to go the extra mile, whether it\'s helping you', time: '6 months ago'}, {author: 'Craig Johnson', rating: 1, text: 'I was disappointed by my purchase. The THC vape pen I purchased was actually a THCA pen. While it has a small amount of THC that comes from all hemp plants it is not what I was looking for when I asked for a THC Vape. I was also told there was a deal for black Friday and I believe I didn\'t get one. I was charged $90 for two pens and the listed price was $39.99 each. I have learned at my own cost t', time: '4 months ago'}, {author: 'Steven Mitchell', rating: 5, text: 'Humble little shop worth your time while up at the north shore! Very friendly customer service and definitely the right vibe from this store.', time: 'a month ago'}, {author: 'Heather Olsen (FeatherWeather)', rating: 5, text: 'We love going to this store. They have fantastic products and great prices. I\'m grateful to have a nice place to get edible, and feel I can trust the recommendations given by the knowledgeable staff.', time: '8 months ago'}, {author: 'Rocks Red', rating: 1, text: 'Have zero prerolls and everything left was 50+ which I probably wouldn’t have minded buying had somewhere on the door or before told me to get enough cash out. I’m not spending $10 a pop on atm fees because a business can’t be bothered to say if they have anything available. I drove two hours to get here. Thanks for wasting my damn time. Unreliable. Over priced and the cheapest green they had was ', time: '8 months ago'}] }
